SMI Corp.  has started closing all
its investment and securities trading accounts to focus on the
entertainment and cinema-operation industry, the company said in
a Hong Kong stock exchange filing today.  The company also amended the terms of its placing agreement
to delete its undertakings to close investment and securities
accounts and not open them again, SMI said. The companyâ€™s stock
